WebLink Privacy Notice for Thailand Residents (English)
helloweblink
2024-03-08T03:40:37+00:00
WebLink
Privacy
Notice
for
Thailand
Residents
Effective Date: March 1, 2024 | Last Updated: March 1, 2024
If you are a Thailand resident, the following will apply:
If you do not provide your personal data which is necessary for us to provide our services to you, you understand that we may not be able to proceed with your request to use our services or comply with our contractual obligation, or if you do not provide your personal data which is necessary for our compliance with applicable laws, it may result in your or our violation of such laws.
In addition to your rights in section 11 (Your Rights and Choices) of this Privacy Policy, you also have the right to file a complaint with the personal data protection authority in accordance with the procedures set out in Thailand Personal Data Protection Law.
